						<div class="postbody">'LAX #immed' isn't even called that, because it doesn't Load A and X. The instruction in its place is sometimes called <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=121065#p121065" class="postlink">ATX</a> instead. Regardless, don't use it.</div>

